'From Squeakland 3.8.5976 of 25 August 2004 [latest update: #348] on 26 January 2005 at 5:48:23 pm'!"Change Set:		FileListRenameFix-nkDate:			26 January 2005Author:			Ned Konzthe FTP rename:toBe: error codes were wrong per RFC 640.This fixes them."!!FTPClient methodsFor: 'protocol' stamp: 'nk 1/26/2005 16:40'!renameFileNamed: oldFileName to: newFileName	self sendCommand: 'RNFR ' , oldFileName.	self lookForCode: 350.	self sendCommand: 'RNTO ' , newFileName.	self lookForCode: 250! !